{
  "texts": [
    "The normalized data range will be between [0, 1].",
    "The third step is data encoding.",
    "Many product design feature data are not in numerical form.",
    "For example, the navigation method of a sweeping robot can be \"laser\", \"gyroscope\", or \"dToF\", and the layout of buttons may include \"up and down layout\" or \"left and right layout\".",
    "Textual data must be converted to numerical data, which is also known as data encoding."
  ]
}